# Linear — Houseplant Hospital 2.0 (exclusive)

This repository **only** relates to work tracked in one Linear workspace.

## Canonical Linear identity

| Field | Value |
|-------|--------|
| **Workspace** | `Houseplant-Hospital` |
| **Issue ID prefix** | `HIL` (e.g. `HIL-1`, `HIL-42`) |

## Rules (strict)

1. **Only `HIL-*` issues** in the **`Houseplant-Hospital`** Linear workspace are valid for this project. Do not reference, create, or update issues from any other Linear workspace or team.
2. If an issue ID does not start with **`HIL`**, it is **out of scope** for this repo — ignore it unless Jack explicitly maps it to a `HIL` issue.
3. When Linear MCP is connected to a different workspace, **do not** use MCP issue data for this project. Jack will provide `HIL-*` IDs or titles, or MCP will be pointed at `Houseplant-Hospital` later.
4. Before non-trivial work: confirm the task exists as a **`HIL`** issue (or ask Jack to create one in `Houseplant-Hospital`).
5. Commits and PR descriptions should reference `HIL-*` when applicable (e.g. `HIL-12: scaffold Supabase schema`).
6. **Task source:** implementation order follows [docs/linear-backlog.md](../../docs/linear-backlog.md). One `HIL` issue per session unless Jack groups them.

Contributor: **jack@jackchalkley.com**. Workflow: [docs/linear-workflow.md](../../docs/linear-workflow.md).
